      "span_text": "Unintentional events led people to seek preventability information, although this link was weaker than the preceding model-implied links, appearing to reflect people's attention to several different concerns when considering unintentional violations -not only determining preventability, but also considering the potential causal involvement of other parties and considering paths toward restitution  ."
